videos.description: Cole Anthony splits defenders on the drive then tosses up an alley-oop for Garrison Brooks who throws it down with two hands.

videos.description: Cole Anthony forces the steal then Armando Bacot caps the break using a Eurostep to stuff down a two-handed dunk.
